          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The experimental set-up consisted of four",
                "particle telescopes,two 12.7 cm*12.7 cm NaI(Tl) and",
                "one Ge(Li) counter.The gamma-ray energy resolution of",
                "the NaI counters was 7%.The Ge(Li) counter had an",
                "efficiency of 20% with a resolution of 2.2 keV at",
                "1.3 MeV.The telescopes were placed at 50 degree with",
                "respect to the beam direction and had front and end Si",
                "counters with thicknesses of 150 mu-m and 3000 mu-m,",
                "respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The dysprosium targets were self-supporting foils",
                "enriched to 90% and 97% in 161Dy and 163Dy,respectively",
                "The target thicknesses were 1.0 mg/cm**2 (161Dy) and",
                "1.7 mg/cm**2 (163Dy)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The authors gave cross sections relative to the elastic",
